{"tid":530752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港豐找換店 - 黑店","createTime":"2018-01-16T06:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T09:50:15.000Z","uid":156183,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a96d2f6ab2db35998647a685788617a71e6b34c","tid":530752,"uid":156183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:00:26.000Z","msg":"聽日公幹趕住去馬來西亞做野，無查過匯率，佢禁機俾2.4 港幣兌一馬來西亞幣俾我， 仲話唔夠，叫我入去坐陣先，唔好走住，另一間拿過黎，唱左$4000 最後俾1666 馬幣我，我之後去其他找換店睇，卜街，間間都2:1 ， 足足差左$700 港幣， 明正言順黑店，附圖一張，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/135954_8afa9faf674054c2d4e98165e6410443.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F135954_8afa9faf674054c2d4e98165e6410443.png&h=0ded5f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家小心呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2d859af573d5619416e7a2404b60ed36fbd8fd","tid":530752,"uid":156183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"大家唱錢小心呢間， 紅招牌"},{"pid":"5fa2b34f1b11157571587573d2cd3f63f8f7b492","tid":530752,"uid":141038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"機場咪仲黑"},{"pid":"8773dc9ad1a06da65fb7e2b430ef4fe72d309687","tid":530752,"uid":151700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"卜咩街呀<br />\n學好廣東話先啦"},{"pid":"72a3d47810dc43ee2c833ebd23e145b995727a66","tid":530752,"uid":156183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:06:35.000Z","msg":"唱4千佢拿我700"},{"pid":"f698d67d9e9fc608af2752d02b7e9819ff23ccfa","tid":530752,"uid":24378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"你自己唔睇匯率走去兌未仲on9，人地又冇揸住槍逼你兌，蝕咗就話人黑店，抵撚你死啦"},{"pid":"341e7b24be7b7ae122db9b5008c9a05b9421fcfb","tid":530752,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"匯率呢家野間唔同一定有...自己唔睇對貴左點都唔算